Create a Stage for checkout in Jenkins Pipeline:

	SCM: Git
	Repo URL: <git-url>
	Credentials: xavy or <as-per-requirement>
	Branch: */master

O/P:

node() {
    stage('Clone') {
        checkout([$class: 'GitSCM', branches: [[name: '*/master']], doGenerateSubmoduleConfigurations: false, extensions: [], submoduleCfg: [], userRemoteConfigs: [[credentialsId: 'f285b507-31d6-4519-964a-3cac3b23370b', url: 'https://github.com/xavyaly/sample-php-project.git']]])
	}
}



